OL,3,CPolice officer held at gunpoint wins
OL,4,Cbravery award
OL,6,FA police officer has been praised for
OL,7,Foutstanding courage after confronting
OL,8,Fan armed offender and helping to
OL,9,Fremove a loaded firearm from the
OL,10,Fstreets.
OL,12,FPC Daniel Clayton, of Greater
OL,13,FManchester Police, has been presented
OL,14,Fwith the Salford Bravery Award for his
OL,15,Factions during a high-risk incident in
OL,16,FAlbert Park on 20 May 2025.
OL,18,FThe drama unfolded when plain-clothed
OL,19,FSalford Challenger officers spotted a
OL,20,Fman on an e-bike wearing a balaclava.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
