FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784191682
OL,3,CPolice officer held at gunpoint wins
OL,4,Cbravery award
OL,6,FThe suspect, later identified as Jay
OL,7,FConway, stole a bike and fled onto
OL,8,FGreat Clowes Street.
OL,10,FAfter hearing a radio alert, PC
OL,11,FClayton quickly deployed and tracked
OL,12,Fdown Conway.
OL,14,FDuring a brief pursuit and struggle,
OL,15,FConway reached for a loaded firearm
OL,16,Fconcealed in his sock and pointed it
OL,17,Fdirectly at the officer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784191682
OL,3,CPolice officer held at gunpoint wins
OL,4,Cbravery award
OL,6,FDespite the immediate threat to his
OL,7,Flife, PC Clayton remained calm, issued
OL,8,Fcommands, and tactically retreated,
OL,9,Fall while the offender continued to
OL,10,Faim the weapon at him.
OL,12,FThanks to PC Clayton's detailed
OL,13,Fdescriptions and professionalism,
OL,14,FConway was arrested by the Salford
OL,15,FChallenger Team and Wanted Unit just
OL,16,F24 hours later, following an extensive
OL,17,Finvestigation using forensic analysis
OL,18,Fand CCTV.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784191682
OL,3,CPolice officer held at gunpoint wins
OL,4,Cbravery award
OL,6,FConway has since been jailed for 14
OL,7,Fyears for possession of a firearm with
OL,8,Fintent to endanger life.
OL,10,FReflecting on the incident, PC Clayton
OL,11,Fsaid: "I am honoured to receive this
OL,12,Faward for bravery after what happened.
OL,14,F"It was a challenging and difficult
OL,15,Fsituation that I was in and under
OL,16,Fextreme pressure, but I am proud of
OL,17,Fhow I acted and as a result it led to
OL,18,Fa loaded firearm being taken off our
OL,19,Fstreets and reduced any further risk
OL,20,Fto the public."
OL,26,@sD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
