CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784191682
OL,3,CPolice officer held at gunpoint wins
OL,4,Cbravery award
OL,6,FHe continued to say: "I am proud of
OL,7,Fwhat I do working for Greater
OL,8,FManchester Police and will always
OL,9,Fremain my priority to act upon
OL,10,Fsituations which pose any risk to the
OL,11,Fpublic, as it is my job to protect the
OL,12,Fcommunity and bring justice to these
OL,13,Foffenders."
OL,26,@nD@VOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
