PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784191682
OL,3,CPolice officer held at gunpoint wins
OL,4,Cbravery award
OL,6,FInspector Matt Christian said: "PC
OL,7,FClayton's conduct on that day
OL,8,Fexemplifies the highest standards of
OL,9,Fpolicing. Faced with a sudden, life-
OL,10,Fthreatening confrontation involving a
OL,11,Floaded firearm at close range, he
OL,12,Fshowed extraordinary courage,
OL,13,Fresilience and professionalism."
OL,15,FSalford District Commander Neil
OL,16,FBlackwood added: "Dan epitomises
OL,17,Fbravery. The courage, professionalism
OL,18,Fand selflessness he displayed that day
OL,19,Fwere exceptional."
OL,26,@nD@`OUuD@`O]xD@ROU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
