OL,3,CPolice officer held at gunpoint wins
OL,4,Cbravery award
OL,6,FPC Clayton is set to appear on
OL,7,FCrimewatch later this year to talk
OL,8,Fabout his experience and the pride he
OL,9,Ftakes in his work protecting the
OL,10,FSalford community.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
